    Matthew "Goose" Gisi (born May 11, 2004) is an American player who currently plays for Illinois State University.

    Trivia

    • Goose won the 2021-2022 "Wisconsin All-State MVP" Award after completing his Senior year as Varsity Captain, leading the team to a 58-0 Record across tournaments.
    • Goose serves as an Esports Facility Supervisor (EFS), Broadcast & Production Coordinator, Social Media Manager, Club President, Club Treasurer, & Club Competitive Coordinator at Illinois State University
    • Goose has a trading card in the "International Esports Hall of Fame"
    • Goose did not lose a single map his last 2 years of High School Scholastic Competition
